Hello Developer,

  you have to first create virtual enviroment in particular folder using following command in windows.
  python3 -m venv venv
  
  Activate it
  venv/Scripts/activate
  
  Install django in same directory
  pip install django
  
  
  now you are ready to use django's features
  
  first create project and then create app.
  
  Thank you :)
  
